ashsimeq 6100\backslash,\backslashmathrm{\{}K{\}}{\$}, and {\$}T{\_}\backslashmathrm{\{}C{\}}{\textless}5000\backslash,\backslashmathrm{\{}K{\}}{\$}. Implication for the formation scenario of close binaries is briefly discussed.},
