e used to derive accurate properties of candidate old and accreting young stellar objects in star-forming regions. We also discuss how a similarly accurate determination of stellar properties can be obtained through a combination of photometric and spectroscopic data. This work is based on observations collected at the European Southern Observatory, Chile (Pr.Id. 288.C-5038, 089.C-0840, 090.C-0050).},
